lines.text: Judge Ito! Have some of my burrito
If a small taco is a taquito, then a small judge... must be a Judge Ito!

[brining breakfest to Tommy]
Wakey wakey, Eggs and Bacey, Time to get up puddin'
Free Willy, Billy. Not Kill Willy, Billy.

[Upon finding his jury summons in the dumpster]
Aha! Court is now in session.
They're serving tuna salad for lunch! Tuna salad for LUNCH!
